text: Sinustrombus is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Strombidae, the true conchs. ==Species== Species within the genus Sinustrombus include: *S. latissimus (Linnaeus, 1758) *S. sinuatus (Lightfoot, 1786) *S. taurus (Reeve, 1857) ==References== Category:Strombidae
title: Sinustrombus
